#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn54.20"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn54.20:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 54 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 54 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn54.20:0.2"
msgid "2. Dutiyavagga "
msgstr "2. The Second Chapter "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn54.20:0.3"
msgid "20. Āsavakkhayasutta "
msgstr "20. The Ending of Defilements "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.341, sc1
msgctxt "sn54.20:1.1"
msgid "“… Āsavānaṃ khayāya saṃvattati. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, when immersion due to mindfulness of breathing is developed and cultivated it leads to the ending of defilements. "

msgctxt "sn54.20:1.2"
msgid "Kathaṃ bhāvito ca, bhikkhave, ānāpānassatisamādhi kathaṃ bahulīkato saṃyojanappahānāya saṃvattati … "
msgstr "And how is immersion due to mindfulness of breathing developed and cultivated so as to lead to giving up the fetters, "

msgctxt "sn54.20:1.3"
msgid "anusayasamugghātāya saṃvattati … "
msgstr "uprooting the underlying tendencies, "

msgctxt "sn54.20:1.4"
msgid "addhānapariññāya saṃvattati … "
msgstr "completely understanding the course of time, "

msgctxt "sn54.20:1.5"
msgid "āsavānaṃ khayāya saṃvattati? "
msgstr "and ending the defilements? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn54.20:1.6"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu araññagato vā rukkhamūlagato vā … pe … "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant—gone to a wilderness, or to the root of a tree, or to an empty hut—sits down cross-legged, with their body straight, and focuses their mindfulness right there. … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn54.20:1.7"
msgid "paṭinissaggānupassī assasissāmīti sikkhati, paṭinissaggānupassī passasissāmīti sikkhati. "
msgstr "They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe in observing letting go.’ They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe out observing letting go.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn54.20:1.8"
msgid "Evaṃ bhāvito kho, bhikkhave, ānāpānassatisamādhi evaṃ bahulīkato saṃyojanappahānāya saṃvattati … pe … "
msgstr "That’s how immersion due to mindfulness of breathing is developed and cultivated so as to lead to giving up the fetters, "

msgctxt "sn54.20:1.9"
msgid "anusayasamugghātāya saṃvattati … pe … "
msgstr "uprooting the underlying tendencies, "

msgctxt "sn54.20:1.10"
msgid "addhānapariññāya saṃvattati … pe … "
msgstr "completely understanding the course of time, "

msgctxt "sn54.20:1.11"
msgid "āsavānaṃ khayāya saṃvattatī”ti. "
msgstr "and ending the defilements.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn54.20:1.12"
msgid "Dasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn54.20:1.13"
msgid "Dutiyo vaggo. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn54.20:2.1"
msgid "Icchānaṅgalaṃ kaṅkheyyaṃ, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn54.20:2.2"
msgid "ānandā apare duve; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn54.20:2.3"
msgid "Bhikkhū saṃyojanānusayā, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn54.20:2.4"
msgid "addhānaṃ āsavakkhayanti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "sn54.20:2.5"
msgid "Ānāpānasaṃyuttaṃ dasamaṃ. "
msgstr "The Linked Discourses on Mindfulness of Breathing is the tenth section."

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
